Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:35.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, in a crazy dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.20,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was gazin' up to the Promised Land
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:41.83,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らのユメの形　ザワメキ出す Heart！ Beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:43.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on let's go to that place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:45.80,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stop anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:50.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛びだせ　仄暗い空　fly into the light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:54.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じたいこの世界に生まれたことが幸せってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:57.07,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代へ続く扉を開けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:59.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:02.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なぁ、わかってるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:05.75,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らはいつだって傷だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみのルーツ断ち切って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怖くないよ　いつでも傍に感じるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:14.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　もっと　もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:18.80,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い　力が心満たしてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.87,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:23.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake！ Up！ Your！ Heart！ Beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:26.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.61,0:01:28.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて Burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:30.39,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brave and boiling heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:33.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆を示せ High！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:35.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:37.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて Burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Boost！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:39.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real deal！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:40.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No more liars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:41.91,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ignition's ON, my heart is on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fire Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:45.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My blood will burn on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:48.28,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah fight on！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:35.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我还是个孩子 在一个疯狂的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正仰望着那块约定之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:41.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的梦的形状 喧嚣四起 心脏起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:43.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我们共同前往那块土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:45.80,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:50.60,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃吧 穿过白日阴沉 飞入光芒 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:54.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信出生于这个世界是一件幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:57.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开通往新时代的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:59.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:02.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你是知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:05.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力斩断悲伤的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕 我们永远能在身边感受到彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:14.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 更多 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:18.80,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将更多炙热的力量填满心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:23.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒你的心跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:26.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.61,0:01:28.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动  燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:30.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢而沸腾的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:33.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现彼此的羁绊 高涨！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:35.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:37.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动  燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速到极限！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:39.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是来真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:40.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要更多谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:41.91,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置已点火 心脏已起搏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰 火焰 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:45.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的热血将燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:48.28,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开战吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:37.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…and so, we met in the deep dark and shattered place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:44.59,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one will come to us. They left us here with disgrace
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:46.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:50.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We all abanded sadness. We all abanded kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:54.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The world is full of hatred. There's no hope, then take this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:58.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘で建った塔の　深層で燃える炎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.13,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（早々気を付けろ背後） 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:01.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:05.31,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready. Burn up！ Liars！ In this cold night
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:08.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただで消え去る罪など無い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.97,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby, cry out louder to this bad luck
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:17.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,God, hear the scream, share us your light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:24.43,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, now stand up and head up cause we're falling up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:20.79,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（Who is the bloody liar？ You all the bloody liar）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:28.48,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創傷疼いている　何故痛いくらい 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:34.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah 今疼き出す…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:41.69,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's behind the truth. We know what we gotta do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:49.72,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's behind the truth. We know what we gotta do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:37.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们相遇在这个深幽破碎之境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:44.59,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会来 他们把我们留在这蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:46.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是孤独的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:50.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀遗弃了我们 仁慈遗弃了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:54.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界充满着憎恶 没有希望 执此前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:58.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用谎言树立的塔 在其深处燃烧的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,50)}（随时小心身后）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:01.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:05.31,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好准备 燃烧吧骗子！在这冰冷的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:08.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赎罪必须付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.97,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 宝贝 为你的厄运大声哭喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:17.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主啊 请聆听这哭号 赐下您的圣光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:24.43,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜 匍匐跌倒之人请起身抬头吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:20.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,50)}（谁是可恶的骗子？你们全是可恶的骗子）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:28.48,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创伤在隐隐作痛 为何如此痛彻心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:34.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 此刻疼痛再起...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:41.69,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真相背后的故事 我们知道我们将做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:49.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真相背后的故事 我们知道我们将做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王舞...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是大人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 黄金！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你不能原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 成功了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 王舞在等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金..酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金酱才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等..又..讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你..你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方知不知羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱是世界通用的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这 这是..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 毕竟东酱一直都待在国外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:49.92,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的年轻人真是没规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:51.85,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国外长大的就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:56.12,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是对他网开一面如何？木乃亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“喂 我才不是在保护你”它说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 但是道谢总是要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答我一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞武器是生物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还要废话到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩骨头了啊 这个情况不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干干瘪瘪 营养不足吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可没法去见母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的舞武器拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你把心脏拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏怎么能拱手让人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别贫嘴 废话少说快拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比你更会使用心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我的心脏 你却更会使用？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧你？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 你在戏弄我么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊君 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说的根本不是同一件事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为东酱他好像连舞武器是什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 也拥有类似这样的东西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 我就知道是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是心脏之人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能撤退了 好不容易来到这里的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 错过这次机会就没有下回了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你掉至地面至今已过十年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为一直待在海外就能装成一无所知的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的什么都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞武器也是今天第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 柊君！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞武器会因主人的危机而做出反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别掩着藏着 亮出来看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 柊君和东酱怎能起打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你那一股子臊气的拳头能打倒我么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为帮老爸报了仇 很开心么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的闹剧一定让你觉得挺自豪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次睁大眼睛瞧着吧 心爱的右手酱的死状
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 站着都吃力的小鬼么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 东酱快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母亲是破坏世界的罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的罪孽由你来偿还吧 用你的这条命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只宠物 调教得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊 它要在这里和主人说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉身碎骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 要做还是做得到的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手酱？右手酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..我认识那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是过去让上野化为火海的家伙的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 一群杂鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧你们的熊样 礼央子的走狗们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不准你用母亲的王舞做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫柊对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你叫东是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你这个当心脏的太不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只好自由发挥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛 我倒也更喜欢一直自由自在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要..有当心脏的样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 果然来得够快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 刚才问我为什么要做这种事对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告诉你那个理由吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是为了引出那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的..舞乱伎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了啊 万流礼央子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 汀的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:14.98,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}第二话 炎之巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 把炎帝击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明礼央子的邪恶本质吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎帝在24年前的战斗中失去了手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它应该发挥不出原本的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 看这样有戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子 明明同为舞武器使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却背叛了舞武器使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的背叛 其他舞武器使全被当成了反叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是真正的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你 让我的父亲发了疯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夺走了父亲身为舞武器使的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要夺回父亲的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来摧毁你建立起的统治体制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来夺回被你葬送的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来..由我来..由我来！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要把所谓的真相..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和只剩骨头的舞乱伎一起从坟墓里挖出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就把你们和王舞一起化为枯骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们的五脏六腑彻底沸腾 蒸发殆尽吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮小鬼们 这下肯定活不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这明明不是原本的力量啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一希汀犯下的罪孽 永远都不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊？为什么认识我的母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长着一双和我最讨厌的女人一样的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我恶心的想吐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金酱 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金酱 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃酱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到黄金他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来怎么办？队长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊 别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们乖乖按照我的指示办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的王舞就不会输给炎帝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理 你的意思是我们的错？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错啊 是你们拖了我的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帮没用的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 别对舞武器撒气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？它们不过是道具而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不会说话也没有痛觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿你的屁股代替它们让我踢几脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 来试试看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊君 木乃酱 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是我们吵架的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我会罢手的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过得让我先揍这家伙一拳再说！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎帝？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汀的儿子 有个好消息告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从漂浮在空中的舞乱伎巢穴中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一台舞乱伎坠落地面 这可是十年来从未有过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这十年来一直在防止舞乱伎坠落地面的你的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一希汀的生命已经走到尽头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一希汀她..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让汀一个人上路太孤单了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你马上去追随她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的火力 这下看来没戏唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正要死的话 至少把我烤成可口的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间就会化成灰烬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 事情变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没有找你来的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 黄金酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她死了的话 坠落的舞乱伎应该不止一台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的人都把我的母亲称为魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是母亲不是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲现在也孤身一人在宝岛努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保护这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次轮到我用王舞登上宝岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来保护母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不像马上要被烧死之人的台词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们都不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金酱 还有各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们从没有把我的母亲称为魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让我很开心 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞武器 舞乱伎的手足
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是它的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.18,0:17:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们的力量借给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们的舞武器托付给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托付给担当心脏的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱 我..我..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 做女人要干脆 应下了 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是朋友的请求..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要帮你这家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 男人别啰哩啰嗦的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆敢敌视我万流礼央子和炎帝的一希之血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只消将其斩草除根！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全敌不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的力量完全不起作用么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 五个人各自行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一个人都战胜不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 大家齐心协力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右脚 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左脚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别喊得那么得瑟！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 要飞咯 右手酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:19:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用炎帝去扫荡坠落地面的舞乱伎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备好列车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 请问小鬼们怎么处置？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管他们 等我处理掉坠落的舞乱伎之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再将他们连同一希汀一起除掉便是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子大人？礼央子大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧开溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承了心脏之舞武器的一希血脉么..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子大人怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 前辈 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但王舞逃之夭夭 连舞武器使的小鬼们都给溜了 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.91,0:23:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.59,0:23:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你礼央子大人的情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都没有变化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子大人的时间依然是停滞不前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和24年前一样 保持着16岁的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不等礼央子大人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子大人交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.85,0:23:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去召集其他的四天王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但王舞被偷 还有舞乱伎坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来事情要变得有趣起来了啊
